-[gear shift clunks]
-[engine revs]

11
00:02:24.012 --> 00:02:26.581
[menacing tone]

12
00:02:42.096 --> 00:02:43.831
-[gasps]
-[brakes squeal]

13
00:02:49.737 --> 00:02:52.640
[honking horn]

14
00:02:56.811 --> 00:03:00.581
-[gear shift clunks]
-[revs engine]

15
00:03:04.052 --> 00:03:05.820
[revs engine]

16
00:03:17.899 --> 00:03:18.966
[metal slicing]

17
00:03:21.268 --> 00:03:23.771
[metal crunching]

18
00:03:36.184 --> 00:03:38.853
[crow cawing]

19
00:03:52.166 --> 00:03:56.537
Yeah. I know
it's Friday night...

20
00:03:57.304 --> 00:03:59.306
[sighs] Stace...

21
00:04:00.875 --> 00:04:03.177
Stacey! [scoffs]

22
00:04:03.310 --> 00:04:05.378
