coming back late.

26
00:04:11.986 --> 00:04:15.422
[baby crying on monitor]

27
00:04:15.489 --> 00:04:18.726
Oh. Sounds like he woke up.

28
00:04:19.493 --> 00:04:20.728
I better check on him.

29
00:04:20.795 --> 00:04:22.797
I have to go.
I'm sorry. have fun.

30
00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:28.736
[door creaks]

31
00:04:56.564 --> 00:04:59.499
[phone rings]

32
00:05:09.442 --> 00:05:10.745
Hello?

33
00:05:10.812 --> 00:05:13.147
[man on phone]
<i>Aren't you scared.</i>

34
00:05:13.214 --> 00:05:16.449
<i>all alone in a big house?</i>

35
00:05:16.517 --> 00:05:18.219
This isn't funny. who are you?

36
00:05:18.286 --> 00:05:21.388
[man on phone] <i>What's funny</i>
<i>is the look on your face.</i>

37
00:05:21.454 --> 00:05:22.957
<i>right now.</i>

38
00:05:25.092 --> 00:05:27.094
<i>What's the matter?</i>

39
00:05:27.161 --> 00:05:28.996
<i>Cat got your tongue?</i>

40
00:05:29.931 --> 00:05:33.768
<i>Or are you scared</i>
<i>I'll wake up the baby?</i>

41
00:05:35.169 --> 00:05:36.704
I'm calling the police.

42
00:05:38.506 --> 00:05:41.441
-[gasps]
-[phone ringing]

43
00:05:43.410 --> 00:05:45.412
[connects call]

44
00:05:51.586 --> 00:05:53.120
What do you want?

45
00:05:53.187 --> 00:05:56.090
[man on phone]
<i>You hang up the phone.</i>

46
00:05:56.157 --> 00:05:57.892
<i>That was rude.</i>

47
00:05:59.193 --> 00:06:01.028
<i>I am on my way.</i>

48
00:06:02.063 --> 00:06:06.100
<i>I don't think the police</i>
<i>will make it on time. Laura.</i>

49
00:06:07.335 --> 00:06:10.671
<i>I am closer than you think.</i>

50
00:06:10.738 --> 00:06:14.141
<i>I can practically smell you.</i>

51
00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:22.049
Why are you doing this?

52
00:06:22.116 --> 00:06:23.450
Where are you?

53
00:06:24.285 --> 00:06:26.153
<i>Knock. knock.</i>

54
00:06:26.220 --> 00:06:27.855
[knocks on door]

55
00:06:57.084 --> 00:06:59.486
[laughing]

56
00:07:02.623 --> 00:07:03.824
[distorted]
We gotcha!

57
00:07:03.891 --> 00:07:06.093
You should see your face. girl.

58
00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:07.395
You're so stupid...

59
00:07:07.494 --> 00:07:10.031
Come on. [kisses]

60
00:07:10.097 --> 00:07:12.066
[chuckling]

61
00:07:12.133 --> 00:07:14.902
[footsteps receding]

62
00:07:14.969 --> 00:07:17.605
[rap music]

63
00:07:20.241 --> 00:07:24.278
-Oh. my God!
-Shut up!

64
00:07:24.345 --> 00:07:26.881
-Oh. this house!
-[laughs]

65
00:07:29.517 --> 00:07:31.152
So enigmatic...

66
00:07:32.053 --> 00:07:33.921
Does your boss
really live here?

67
00:07:33.988 --> 00:07:36.824
Oh. my gosh. yeah!
Really enigmatic!

68
00:07:36.891 --> 00:07:40.528
And actually perfect for what
I have planned for us tonight.

69
00:07:40.561 --> 00:07:41.996
[Laura] So. what is it
this time?

70
00:07:42.063 --> 00:07:44.865
Hunter told me about
this crazy challenge

71
00:07:44.932 --> 00:07:47.101
that's blowing up
on social media.

72
00:07:47.168 --> 00:07:49.270
It's called
the Baby Blue Challenge

73
00:07:49.337 --> 00:07:51.672
and it's creepy as fuck!

74
00:07:51.739 --> 00:07:53.607
Hunter. I should have known.

75
00:07:54.408 --> 00:07:56.010
Okay. what's it about?

76
00:07:56.077 --> 00:07:59.647
So. in order to play
the Baby Blue Challenge.

77
00:07:59.714 --> 00:08:02.216
we need to go to the bathroom.

78
00:08:02.283 --> 00:08:04.118
turn off all the lights.

79
00:08:04.185 --> 00:08:05.720
lock the door.

80
00:08:05.786 --> 00:08:08.589
and it's actually recommended
to do it at night

81
00:08:08.656 --> 00:08:11.559
so there is
absolutely no light.

82
00:08:11.625 --> 00:08:13.327
We've got the most
important part done!

83
00:08:13.394 --> 00:08:16.764
It's night time! And I'm
assuming we have a bathroom.

84
00:08:17.598 --> 00:08:20.067
[laughs] I'm just kidding.

85
00:08:20.134 --> 00:08:22.203
Okay. continue please.

86
00:08:22.269 --> 00:08:23.604
Sure.

87
00:08:24.372 --> 00:08:25.673
So...

88
00:08:26.574 --> 00:08:31.445
there is said to be two ways
to do the Baby Blue Challenge.

89
00:08:31.579 --> 00:08:33.047
The first way.

90
00:08:33.114 --> 00:08:36.617
you need to begin
by telling a horror story.

91
00:08:36.684 --> 00:08:39.487
Then.
you proceed to the bathroom.

92
00:08:39.587 --> 00:08:42.757
face the mirror
and light up a candle.

93
00:08:44.025 --> 00:08:47.962
Then. you need to
position your arms like this.

94
00:08:48.029 --> 00:08:50.965
just as if you were
cradling a baby.

95
00:08:51.665 --> 00:08:53.300
And meanwhile.

96
00:08:53.367 --> 00:08:55.803
you need speak the phrase.

97
00:08:55.870 --> 00:08:58.439
"Baby blue. blue baby."

98
00:08:58.507 --> 00:09:00.608
thirteen times.

99
00:09:01.675 --> 00:09:03.811
If you do everything right.

100
00:09:03.878 --> 00:09:06.480
you will begin
to feel how your arms

101
00:09:06.614 --> 00:09:10.084
are getting heavier.
and heavier.

102
00:09:10.151 --> 00:09:14.655
Just as if you were
actually holding a baby.

103
00:09:14.722 --> 00:09:16.991
[scoffs]
But that is not all. love.

104
00:09:17.058 --> 00:09:19.927
At one point you're gonna
start to feel.

105
00:09:19.994 --> 00:09:24.799
how it's trying
to crawl up your chest.

106
00:09:24.865 --> 00:09:28.069
your shoulders. your neck.

107
00:09:28.135 --> 00:09:31.305
as if he wanted us
to see him...

108
00:09:31.372 --> 00:09:34.809
face. to face.

109
00:09:34.875 --> 00:09:37.978
Oh. but bitch.
before it is too late.

110
00:09:38.045 --> 00:09:39.947
you need to release the baby.

111
00:09:40.014 --> 00:09:43.552
And what happens if we
don't let the baby go on time?

112
00:09:43.651 --> 00:09:46.754
[chuckles]
You're gonna love this.

113
00:09:46.821 --> 00:09:49.090
If you don't do it fast enough.

114
00:09:50.024 --> 00:09:54.261
they say a horrible woman
will appear in the mirror.

115
00:09:54.328 --> 00:09:56.797
demanding her baby back.

116
00:09:57.331 --> 00:10:01.102
Legend has it.
that a long. long time ago.

117
00:10:01.168 --> 00:10:05.239
this mother
carelessly drowned her baby

118
00:10:05.306 --> 00:10:06.907
in a bathtub.

119
00:10:06.974 --> 00:10:09.944
She left him unattended.

120
00:10:10.010 --> 00:10:11.679
And when she returned.

121
00:10:12.646 --> 00:10:14.482
her baby was dead.

122
00:10:14.549 --> 00:10:16.851
Drowned underwater.

123
00:10:16.917 --> 00:10:21.322
and it had completely
turned blue.

124
00:10:22.756 --> 00:10:25.359
Ew. the baby turned blue?
That's so gross.

125
00:10:26.093 --> 00:10:28.462
But the color blue
does look good on me.

126
00:10:28.530 --> 00:10:31.098
[laughs] Stacey.

127
00:10:31.165 --> 00:10:34.301
Yeah. but the mother
couldn't bear the pain.

128
00:10:34.368 --> 00:10:38.139
so she broke the mirror.
and slit her wrists!

129
00:10:38.672 --> 00:10:41.041
And now.

130
00:10:41.108 --> 00:10:45.813
two restless souls of
this mother and her baby

131
00:10:45.880 --> 00:10:47.848
can be summoned

132
00:10:47.915 --> 00:10:51.785
if you do exactly
what I just said.

133
00:10:53.053 --> 00:10:55.356
So. who wants to go first?

134
00:10:56.625 --> 00:10:58.159
Not me.

135
00:11:01.228 --> 00:11:02.597
Okay. I'll go.

136
00:11:02.730 --> 00:11:04.798
And please girls.
while I'm gone.

137
00:11:04.865 --> 00:11:08.402
try to master some courage.
please? [chuckles]

138
00:11:08.469 --> 00:11:10.070
Laura. where is the bathroom?

139
00:11:10.137 --> 00:11:12.940
Um. it's down the hall
to the left.

140
00:11:14.609 --> 00:11:16.110
[Maureen]
Bye-bye. ladies.

141
00:11:16.177 --> 00:11:17.211
[Stacey]
Bye.

142
00:11:18.012 --> 00:11:20.247
Good luck! [laughs]

143
00:11:26.253 --> 00:11:28.155
[chuckles] Cool.

144
00:11:38.533 --> 00:11:39.833
[exhales]

145
00:11:39.900 --> 00:11:42.203
[flicks lighter]

146
00:11:53.548 --> 00:11:54.583
So.

147
00:11:55.382 --> 00:11:59.086
