226
00:17:33.588 --> 00:17:35.188
[panting]

227
00:17:35.890 --> 00:17:39.493
[distorted voice]

228
00:17:39.561 --> 00:17:40.828
Okay.

229
00:17:53.608 --> 00:17:56.310
Okay. Oh. my God.

230
00:18:01.749 --> 00:18:02.784
[grunts]

231
