Inside.

234
00:18:34.582 --> 00:18:36.483
Inside.

235
00:18:36.551 --> 00:18:38.452
Inside.

236
00:18:38.519 --> 00:18:40.622
Inside.

237
00:18:40.688 --> 00:18:42.857
-Inside.
-Stop!

238
00:18:42.924 --> 00:18:44.926
Inside.

239
00:18:44.993 --> 00:18:46.995
-Inside...
-Stop it now!

240
00:18:47.061 --> 00:18:48.997
Inside.

241
00:18:49.063 --> 00:18:50.898
-Val!
-Inside.

242
00:18:52.100 --> 00:18:54.535
No! [panting]

243
00:18:54.602 --> 00:18:57.270
Oh. my God.
Just leave me alone!

244
00:18:59.239 --> 00:19:00.474
Get away from me!

245
00:19:02.209 --> 00:19:03.544
Stop. please.

246
00:19:04.879 --> 00:19:06.881
